How is the equilibrium constant expressed for high-pressure gas reactions? Is $\prod_B \left( rac{p_B^{	ext{eq}}}{p^{	heta}}ight)^{
u_B}$ for high-pressure gas reactions only a function of temperature? Is $\prod_B \left( rac{p_B^{	ext{eq}}}{p^{	heta}}ight)^{
